## Presigned URLs

Generate a temporary URL that allows someone to access or upload an object without AWS credentials.

```bash
# Presigned URL valid for 1 hour (download)
aws s3 presign s3://my-app-bucket-joon/report.pdf --expires-in 3600

# Presigned URL for upload (via SDK — CLI does not support PUT presign directly)
```

Common use case: your app generates a presigned URL and sends it to a client so they can upload directly to S3 without going through your server.

